Titolo: Lockheart Indigo

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Lockheart Indigo is an independent adventure game developed by Harmless Games. It is a neo-noir psychological thriller that's visually styled after 8-bit video games such as those on the Game Boy Color, using limited colors with a pixel art aesthetic.The player controls Beatris Summers, a young private detective hired to solve the murder of the business owner, known as Evan Volkov. Beatris must attempt to interrogate one of the residents who commit the crime behind the wealthy robotics tycoon in the mansion.
The game was released commercially on July 31, 2020 on Steam and itch.io. It was made available as freeware on December 21, 2020.

